a K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Foday, Ibrahim", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Johnny, Jonathan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bakarr, Ibrahim A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Whitmer, Shannon L. M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wright, Emily A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gbakima, Aiah A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Graziano, James", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bangura, Camilla", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kamanda, Emmanuel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Osborne, Augustus", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Saidu, Emmanuel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Musa, Jonathan A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bangura, Doris F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Williams, Sammuel M. T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fefegula, George M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sumaila, Christian", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jabaty, Juliet", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "James, Fatmata H.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jambai, Amara", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Garnett, Kate", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kamara, Thomas F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Towner, Jonathan S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lebbie, Aiah", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/4288221a2be976dca375b37d5e598cfb", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/e24e5e88e2bdb396b3fd350d2f75608d8855fb3dfefcdc3d5a274157c7e89348", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/3UBL8BRA", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/3UBL8BRA", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/6197da5b40663f99e329f551b074cdd7!/b7-2468", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f49